title: It's Year 3 of the COVID-19 Pandemic. What Should We Expect?
description: MarketWatch personal-finance editor Quentin Fottrell talks to Dr. Gregory Poland, who studies the immunogenetics of vaccine response at the Mayo Clinic, about the trajectory of the pandemic.
